description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Spring - Flower garden in Sapporo
-Spring - Rape blossom fields in Abira
-Spring - Cherry blossom trees in Ishikari
-Summer - Shikotsu Lake
-Summer - Cape Kamui
-Summer - Lavender fields at Houmi Pass
-Autumn - Hills of Biei
-Autumn - Sapporo Autumn Foliage
-Winter - Ice bubble on Nukabira Lake
-Winter - Lake Toya
